								<p class="pb15 text-justify">We wish to ensure your personal information is complete, accurate and up to date. Needyin allows you to change or correct your personal information at any time. To do so, simply log into your Needyin account, and you will find options for editing the information you have submitted.</p>  
                             	
								<h4 class="h4 fbold txt-blue">Access to Personal Information</h4>   
